					Full Description



		Megalogic Technology Holdings Limited is a Hong Kong-based investment holding company principally engaged in the development and sales of integrated circuits (IC). The Company operates through two segments. IC segment is engaged in the sales of ICs under the brand of MiniLogic, as well as the provision of design and development services of ICs. Its IC products are applied in power management, light-emitting diode (LED) drivers, electronic cigars and digital video disk players, among others. Money Lending segment is engaged in money lending businesses, such as the provision of secured and unsecured loans to customers to earn interest income. The Company operates businesses in China, Korea, the United States of America and Russia, among others.
» Full Overview of 8242.HK







