                                                Megalogic Technology Holdings Ltd
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Megalogic Technology Holdings Ltd operates in the Semiconductors and related devices sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Megalogic Technology Holdings Ltd with three other
	
			companies in this sector in Hong Kong:
		
	International Standard Resources Holdings Ltd
	
		(2016
	sales of 23.52 million Hong Kong Dollars [US$3.01  million]
		of which 87%
		was Electronic Components),
	
	Jun Yang Financial Holdings Ltd
	
		(70.56 million Hong Kong Dollars [US$9.03  million]
		), and
	
	Heng Xin China Holdings Ltd
	
		(81.22 million Hong Kong Dollars [US$10.40  million]
		of which 76%
		was Wireless Digital Television Value-Added ).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	Megalogic Technology Holdings Ltd reported sales of HK$60.75 million (US$7.78 million)
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
				an
			
			increase of 107.7%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were HK$29.24 million.
	
		The sales level in 2016 was fairly close to the level five years ago: in 2011, Megalogic Technology Holdings Ltd had sales
		of HK$59.13 million.
	

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










